column2: SELECT   S.ra, S.dec,   S.mjd, S.plate, S.fiberID, S.class,    S.z, S.zErr, S.rChi2, S.velDisp, S.velDispErr, dbo.fgeturlfitsspectrum(S.specobjid),   G.extinction_r, G.petroMag_r, G.psfMag_r, G.psfMagErr_r,   G.modelMag_u, G.modelMagErr_u, G.modelMag_g, G.modelMagErr_g,   G.modelMag_r, G.modelMagErr_r, G.modelMag_i, G.modelMagErr_i,   G.modelMag_z, G.modelMagErr_z, G.petroR5#_r, G.petroR9#_r,   GSL.oii_#_flux, GSL.oii_#_flux_err,    GSL.neiii_#_flux, GSL.neiii_#_flux_err,   GSL.h_gamma_flux, GSL.h_gamma_flux_err,   GSL.nii_#_flux, GSL.nii_#_flux_err,    GSL.h_alpha_flux, GSL.h_alpha_flux_err,    GSL.oiii_#_flux, GSL.oiii_#_flux_err,   GSL.h_beta_flux, GSL.h_beta_flux_err,    GSL.h_delta_flux, GSL.h_delta_flux_err,    GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err,   GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err,     GSX.d4#, GSX.d4#_err, GSE.bptclass,   GSE.lgm_tot_p5#, GSE.sfr_tot_p5#, G.objID, GSI.specObjID   INTO MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss_details2 FROM MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss AS m     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj S ON S.specObjID = m.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN Galaxy G ON G.specObjID = S.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN GalSpecInfo GSI ON GSI.specObjID = S.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN GalSpecLine GSL ON GSL.specObjID = S.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN GalSpecIndx GSX ON GSX.specObjID = S.specObjID     LEFT OUTER JOIN GalSpecExtra GSE ON GSE.specObjID = S.specObjID
